OL,3,CMan jailed after stabbing family
OL,4,Cmembers in care home
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for stabbing
OL,7,Fthree of his family members at a care
OL,8,Fhome in before going on the run.
OL,10,FIzoel Crudu broke into the residential
OL,11,Fhome and attacked two of his victims
OL,12,Fwith a knife on 21 December 2022,
OL,13,Fleaving them with slash wounds to
OL,14,Ftheir arms and hands.
OL,16,FThe next day in the early hours of the
OL,17,Fmorning, the 27-year-old was spotted
OL,18,Fby another family member on West
OL,19,FBromwich High Street.
