OL,3,CMan jailed after stabbing family
OL,4,Cmembers in care home
OL,6,FA fight broke-out between the men,
OL,7,Fbefore Crudu stabbed his third victim
OL,8,Fthree times.
OL,10,FHe then fled the scene, leaving his
OL,11,Frelation alone in the street with
OL,12,Fserious injuries.
OL,14,FCrudu went on the run for almost a
OL,15,Fyear before he was arrested in
OL,16,FBlackburn in September 2023.
OL,18,FHe pleaded guilty at Birmingham Crown
OL,19,FCourt, and has been sentenced to eight
OL,20,Fyears and three months in prison.
