OL,6,FDetective Constable Gareth Glass from
OL,7,Fthe Public Protection Unit at West
OL,8,FMidlands Police, said: "Crudu went on
OL,9,Fa violent rampage against his own
OL,10,Ffamily causing them to suffer serious
OL,11,Finjuries.
OL,13,F"We do not tolerate violence of any
OL,14,Fkind, particularly when this involves
OL,15,Fknives, and will do everything in our
OL,16,Fpower to support victims and bring
OL,17,Fperpetrators to justice.
